Do you use your bookmarks as it should be used?

It should be a quick access to some links that are useful to you, but in reality what happens is that you just forget about them after a while because, well, they're not so fast to access.

So this extension comes with the solution for this.

By typing a simple command, you can quickly search through your bookmarks and history to easy navigate to them
